{"tid":1477001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警記者會知法犯法-無視知識產權","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:52:07.000Z","uid":44224,"like":524,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b06f3248fa2564d5e17b02f3a537d8c076bdae","tid":1477001,"uid":44224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"個記者會開始左咁耐點解無人質疑過以下既嘢？<br />\n<br />\n1.黑警發放既相片是否全部都係警方自己拍攝<br />\n<br />\n-經常見到只有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小部份相有credit</span></strong><br />\n-公眾有權知悉相片來源，拍攝者，角度等對相片真確性有好大影響<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.黑警發放既影片是否全部都係警方自己拍攝<br />\n<br />\n-原因大致同上<br />\n-影片有否剪輯過，改動過，警察必須要向公眾交代<br />\n-相片影片原有人有權<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>追究警察未經同意下向公眾發佈</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港警察知法犯法<br />\n請記者今日向記者會本質質詢!"},{"pid":"6931ffc958bb50407bcd95c2cd5c55793158e63e","tid":1477001,"uid":241244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de9de89a1ec287d858b5ee72f490e7223d6cdce6","tid":1477001,"uid":209543,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0b268dd0bfc1269098c8adf70158d64f627723","tid":1477001,"uid":44224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0c5fa7f7912b078337d0a690dda72cc5ee95bf06","tid":1477001,"uid":44224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4580f26f70852bb36da8490d0f9a75044df8e993","tid":1477001,"uid":44224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"堆到熱門"},{"pid":"44da478515b4a8be0b1cbdea80fbe339f8da1fe9","tid":1477001,"uid":13581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16